Contact AAL Recycling Ltd - The company recycles builders waste at La Collette. The company could charge for the service.

Email AAL Recycling Ltd to set up a customer account (their email is listed below)

Or you could contact the Association of Jersey Charities to find out if any local good causes are undergoing building work and need spare bricks.

If your bricks are broken up and are in a bad condition they will need to go into unrecyclable waste. Take it to the inert waste infill site at La Collette. Charges apply.

